KitKat::

She was grabbed by Destructor.  He held her up as he went flying.  
She landed next to him as the blast sent them to the ground.  Despite 
her own injuries, she tried to help him to his feet. "Come on, we 
have to retreat back to base. Neither of us will make it out of this 
fight if we continue. We must go and get maintenanced. Then we shall 
come back and finish the job on another day. Let them have a small 
victory. We still will win the war."  She was having trouble, her 
wounds were leaking heavily. Despite the patch that Carnatron gave 
her, her wounds were still sever. She was down to 25 % before she 
lost consiousness. But her programs were not going to let her give in 
untill her spark stopped.
